The paper deals with information theory and communication channels, which are typically categorized under cs.IT. The use of feedback in the channel also suggests the possibility of it falling under cs.SI (systems and control) or cs.NI (networking and internet architecture). The paper also involves the use of mathematical techniques and proofs, which could place it under cs.CC (computational complexity) or cs.LG (machine learning).
